Hi there everyone!
This is Katie here with the first post in our new journal! I really hope you guys like it, it was alot of work to make. But we are really going to enjoy having it. =D 
I plan on starting a custom mood theme, I just not sure of what yet. I guess i'll have to conference with Miss Alisha. Lemme give you guys an general idea of what I'LL be posting here in the journal. 

-Fanfics
-Banners and Icons
-Random things that happen to me

And pretty much anything else I can think of. LOL! If you add us to your f'list just email me and let me know! I'll frind you right back!
